                            <h5 class="panel-title mb-0"><a href="#collapse-capture-order-statuses" data-bs-toggle="collapse"  class="accordion-toggle collapsed text-dark mb-0" aria-expanded="false">Tamara trigger configuration <i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i></a></h4>
